text:
Why would anyone trust FBI leadership right now?

They broke all the rules in the Trump-Russia probe.

@HouseGOP will hold them accountable.

The Air Force released the personnel military records of two House Republicans to an opposition research firm that received money from the Democratic Congressional Campaign Committee.

This is unethical, and it's likely criminal.

@Weaponization will hold them accountable.

The White House hasn’t been honest with us from the beginning.

Abroad, it makes America look weak. At home, it causes wild speculation.

@POTUS needs to be straightforward with the American people.

The balloon is designed to both gather intel and harass the U.S. before Secretary Blinken’s then-visit to China.

@POTUS should have shot it down the moment it entered our airspace.

The world needs to know that violations of our sovereignty will be met with a strong response.
